c356e552907fca244a97b544e03f6aaabb","tid":1170344,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc8d9fea44a47fce15557277e6a7e7650588fce9","tid":1170344,"uid":121546,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"你想泛民良心發現?<br />\n示威者到時自己提防啦，有糾察隊就當係警察既奸細咁辦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"同時如果有人話某示威搞事/激進或者任何理由拉人走，記得唔好比佢地走<br />\n糾察隊係冇權拉人，同埋到時人多擠迫，小心唔好撞傷踢傷比人帶走既示威者"},{"pid":"0eee0919be0e52c23e20ec76472496cd9e622608","tid":1170344,"uid":60635,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"泛民黃絲有份攪到香港咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你上佢地唔抽刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己小心D好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652045b22ff9246687e1d653feba605df62563cb","tid":1170344,"uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"總之要小心泛民啦<br />\n<br />\nFOOL ME ONCE, SHAME ON YOU<br />\n<br />\nFOOL ME TWICE, SHAME ON ME"},{"pid":"d72ff1ce0dd0193bab3e61c694a1c77354cfca4d","tid":1170344,"uid":121546,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"雖然示威果陣好多人會得閒冇野做拎手機出黎拍片，但係拍到其他示威者個樣就唔好放上網<br />\n我自己都好驚比人影到然後比警察秋後算帳，同埋現場咁多人，手機跌左落地好難搵得返"},{"pid":"ea90e1257fc229aeac78f6f4c0a2fef41d5014c3","tid":1170344,"uid":34144,"like":7,"dislike":18,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"真係壯觀，結論就係留喺屋企打飛機最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母有人唔做走去做三毛狗，你要泛民班撚樣唔好出賣你，你咪去民陣度同班仆街傾囉，喺度扮提醒人實則想叫人唔鳩好出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出去衝嘅咪私下聚一班人食放題，屌那星係都要搞分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c528771482fa76e9